# 18. All matched postings in the displayed intervals should be reported on.
hledgerdev -f- balance -p 'monthly 2014/1/10-2014/2/20'
<<<
2014/1/5
 (before)  1

2014/2/1
 (within)  1

2014/2/25
 (after)  1

>>>
Balance changes in 2014/01/01-2014/02/28:

        ||  2014/01  2014/02 
========++===================
 after  ||        0        1 
 before ||        1        0 
 within ||        0        1 
--------++-------------------
        ||        1        2 

>>>=0
